I’m giving away a Tesla CAR 🚘 Follow the steps below to enter:

1. Go To @highkeyclout

2. Follow everyone @highkeyclout is following. (takes less than 30 seconds)

3. Come back here and comment “Done” when you finish.

Bonus entry: share this post to your story! Tag me & @highkeyclout 🔑

The Winner of the car will be announced by @highkeyclout on their IG story.

This is not sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with, Instagram OR Tesla. The full Sweepstakes Official Rules are available at the link in @highkeyclout bio. #sweepstakes #ad
